','IMG_6137.jpg','',4,6,1,13,'The room before had a brown painted feature wall with beige wall, and was empty of furniture.','A photo of a teal velvet sofa in a room painted off white and on a colourful geometric rug.'),(167,'I','IMG_2263_cropped.jpg','IMG_6134.jpg','',3,6,9,13,'The before photo shows the empty room with a brown painted feature wall and beige walls.','A photo of the velvet chair in front of the windows, with the black planters to the side.'),(168,'I','IMG_2254cropped.jpg','IMG_6136_MTttp4w.jpg','',4,6,13,13,'Before the room had beige walls and a small table with fold out chairs.','A view of the dining table, with the colourful pendant lights and artwork.'),(169,'I','IMG_2270_lighter.jpg','','',3,4,10,13,'','A close up of the vintage artwork, through the tall plant and one of the blue pendant lights.'),(170,'I','IMG_2250_cropped.jpg','','',4,5,12,13,'','A photo of the gallery wall created from specially chosen artwork and personal photos.'),(172,'I','IMG_2278_cropped.jpg','','',2,8,5,13,'','A close up photo of the black floor lamp, which has some brass undertones.'),(173,'I','IMG_2257cropped.jpg','IMG_6136.jpg','',4,8,4,13,'Before the room had beige walls and a small table with fold out chairs.','A photo of the mid century style dining table with upholstered chairs in blue, orange and grey.'),(174,'I','IMG_2280_cropped_more.jpg','','',3,5,6,13,'','A close up of the four glass blown pendant lights in orange and blue.'),(175,'I','IMG_2274_cropped.jpg','IMG_6135_cropped.jpg','',2,6,3,13,'The room before, with no furniture and beige walls.','A photo of the chair by the windows, with two black planters and a personal photo on the wall.'),(176,'I','IMG_2259_cropped.jpg','','',2,8,11,13,'','A photo of the tall plant in a rattan planter, next to the dining table.'),(177,'I','IMG_2246.jpg','IMG_6137_sgSk8tN.jpg','',5,7,14,13,'The room before had a brown painted feature wall with beige wall, and was empty of furniture.','An view of the teal velvet sofa and the