h the striped wallpaper on the ceiling and wall in the background.'),(189,'I','IMG_2299_cropped.jpg','','',2,6,8,14,'','A close up of a child\'s coat hanging on a cactus shaped hook.'),(190,'I','IMG_2305.jpg','','',2,7,3,14,'','A close up view of the white cot with the wallpaper mural and bookshelves in the background.'),(191,'I','IMG_2309_adjusted_straightened.jpg','nursery2.jpg','',5,7,15,14,'Before, this wall was wallpapered in a cream stripe wallpaper and the room was being used for storage.','A view of the animal themed wallpaper mural with the white cot in front and colourful blanket draped over the side.'),(192,'I','IMG_2284_WNfb1Nt.jpg','nursery3.jpg','',5,7,1,14,'The same view of the room before, which was painted magnolia and was used a junk room.','A view of the wallpaper mural, with the white cot in front and the colourful Roman blind at the window.'),(193,'T','','','A spare room has been turned into a playful nursery, brightened up with colour and a charming wall mural, giving the little one lots to look at.',1,6,2,14,'',''),(194,'I','IMG_2298_abacus.jpg','','',2,4,9,14,'','A close up of the rainbow coloured abacus on top of the dresser.'),(195,'T','','','The soft stripe of the wallpaper is taken up and over the ceiling, taking the room out of the ordinary and creating a cocooning effect.',4,1,5,14,'',''),(196,'I','IMG_2312_cropped_more_colour.jpg','','',2,7,7,14,'','A close up a black and white baby sleeping bag hanging on a white hook.'),(197,'T','','','The brief was for a creative, playful, colourful, original, fun and welcoming space. No boring neutrals here!',2,2,11,14,'',''),(198,'T','','','The animal themed wall mural is the star of the show. There are hours of fun to be had making up stories and imagining what the animals are up to - perfect for entertaining the new arrival.',1,7,16,14,'','');
