INSERT INTO `main_site_service` VALUES (1,'Home Consultation','M','Two hours of my time to discuss your ideas, hopes and dreams for your project. Together we\'ll cover budgets, space planning, colour schemes and styles. We\'ll look through some specially chosen samples to discover your interiors taste and I\'ll give you professional advice on the practicalities of making changes to your home or commercial space. \r\n\r\nThis service can be used on its own but I will complete a site survey (including taking measurements and photographs) so that I have everything I need to produce a beautiful interior design if you decide to go ahead to the next stage. It also includes a written report of our meeting so you can put our plan into action.','140 per consultation (plus travel over a 10 mile radius)',1,0,'Treharne_Kitchen_Concept_cropped_no_border_lighter_green_logo_moved.jpg','Book Now','IMG_2462_adjusted_6.jpg'),(2,'Interior Design','M','Includes full layout planning with a scale floor plan, colour schemes, window and flooring treatments, furniture, lighting and accessories all handpicked for you. I produce a sample board so you can see how all the items in your design work together, and visualisations using Sketch Up Pro to show you exactly how your room will look. A full breakdown of costs and a list of all items in your design is also included.\r\n\r\nI can work with any size project budget and will give you a design quote before I begin work, but as a rough guide, the design of one room will typically take between one and two full days depending on the complexity of the project.','55 per hour or a day rate of 300 (8 hours @ 37.50)',2,0,'IMG_20190120_113540_cropped.jpg','','IMG_20190621_112648_correct_size.jpg'),(3,'Procurement','M','When you receive your finished design you will have all the information you need to turn it into reality, or you can choose to let me do all the of ordering for you.\r\nYou make one convenient payment and I will buy all of the items in your design, create an ordering schedule and book deliveries so that your items arrive in time for installation. If there are any problems, I also organise any returns or exchanges, making the process stress free for you. \r\n\r\nYou also get access to my trade discounts which range from 10%-40% of retail prices, and for an extra fee, I can even receive and check all the items being delivered for you, so you don\'t have to wait in for deliveries.','A handling charge of 15% of the retail cost of the goods',3,0,'IMG_1999_cropped_straight.jpg','','Richard__Anni_mood_boards_9jWRo2G.jpg'),(4,'Installation','M','Would you like me to handle the installation of any part of your design? From bringing in a decorator to the installation of bespoke items such as curtains or carpentry, I can organise it all. I will coordinate and supervise all trades involved to ensure your project is finished to a high standard, and any problems are dealt with efficiently. \r\n\r\nMy renovation experience means that I understand the more technical aspects of bringing a design to life, and will communicate with both you and the trades involved to help the project run smoothly.','55 per hour or a day rate of 300 (8 hours @ 37.50)',4,0,'Treharne_Kitchen_Visual_2_for_website.jpg','','Bockelmann-Evans_plans.jpg'),(6,'Online interior design','O','If you like my design style and would like to work with me but don\'t live nearby, my online design service is perfect for you. Here\'s how it works - you fill out my simple questionnaire and send photos, we have a consultation over the phone, and then I get to work and email your finished design package to you. The package includes a scale floorplan, 2D visualisations so that you can see how your new room will look, and all the information you need to implement the design yourself. One hour\'s follow up to make any changes to the design is also included.\r\n\r\nI\'ve worked with clients as far afield as London, Dubai and the Cayman Islands, and together we\'ve produced some stunning results which my clients are delighted with.','450 per room',7,0,'IMG_1994_straight_cropped_again.jpg','',''),(8,'Interior styling','O','The final stage is the styling of your new room. This is often the part that clients struggle with, so let me oversee the finishing touches to make your newly designed room look flawless. I make sure your pictures are hung in the right place, your cherished personal items are displayed to look their best, and all your lovely new accessories are arranged perfectly.\r\n\r\nI can also help with styling if you are selling or letting a property and would you like to increase your chances of attracting a buyer or tenant. I give advice on staging your home so that it looks its best, as a well presented home not only sells more quickly, it can boost the purchase price or rental income.','55 per hour or a day rate of 300 (8 hours @ 37.50)',5,0,'IMG_2012cropped_straightened_4_NiCUX6x.jpg','','');
