INSERT INTO `main_site_siteconfig` VALUES (1,'https://www.instagram.com/louise_m_interiors/','https://www.facebook.com/louise.m.interiors/','https://www.houzz.co.uk/pro/louiseminteriors','https://uk.linkedin.com/in/louise-misell-409261105','https://www.pinterest.co.uk/louisemisell/','Penylan\r\nCardiff','louise@louisemisellinteriors.co.uk','+447811287791','+442920497667','Privacy_Policy_csix9Dy.pdf','Terms_and_Conditions_new_website_1.pdf',3000,10000,'https://twitter.com/l_m_interiors','The latest news, tips and interiors inspiration from Louise Misell Interiors. See my posts about anything from the latest fabric and wallpaper collections to \'how to\' guides for all things interiors related.','Here you can find my contact details or send me a message. You can book a free introductory chat with me or make a home consultation appointment using the online booking form. I look forward to hearing from you.','I\'m a Cardiff based interior designer, offering a full range of design services with clear pricing. I use a clever mix of colour, texture and pattern to create spaces with personality and warmth. I have designed unique room schemes for a wide range of clients across South Wales, including city apartments, holiday rentals and large rural properties.','The design schemes I have produced are bespoke to each client, as I work with you to create an interior which reflects your personality, with an added injection of colour and drama. Have a look at my portfolio to see some past completed work.','Here are the interior design services I offer, from design only to a full project managed by me. I operate on an hourly or day rate basis, with all my prices clearly marked. I can give you as much or as little help as you\'d like, and will tailor my service to your needs.','See what some of my satisfied clients have to say about their experience of working with me, and how I helped them transform their homes into spaces which work practically, and which they love to spend time in.','Who is Louise Misell? Find out all about me - who I am, my education and background, my interior design training, and the reason why I set up my interior design business.','About Louise Misell','Welcome to my design blog, where you\'ll see posts about anything from my current interiors obsession, to the latest fabric and wallpaper collections, and \'how to\' guides for all things interiors related. I love colour and pattern, architecture and old buildings, and I especially love the moment when you see something so beautiful it makes you take a sharp intake of breath. Happy reading, and if you have any questions, or would like to chat about anything interiors related, please use the contact form to get in touch. \r\n\r\nThank you, \r\n\r\nLouise','Blog - news, tips and inspiration','My contact details and how to book','Welcome to Louise Misell Interiors','<p><span style=\"font-size:48px\">Inspiring interior design for real people</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:26px\">Our interior spaces have a huge impact on the way we think and feel, and I believe that everyone deserves an environment which is functional, beautiful and unique. Your home should inspire you, express your personality and help you make the most of the time you spend in it.</span></p>','Inspiring interior design for real people','','My interior design portfolio','I offer a full range of interior design services, and can help you as much or as little as you like. I will come to your home to give you interior design advice as a one off appointment, or if you\'d like more help, I can design your room scheme for you. You can then order items from the scheme yourself, or I can place your orders and arrange deliveries. If you need tradespeople to carry out work, I can call in trusted professionals to do anything from hanging pictures, installing bathrooms, making curtains or building bespoke bookshelves. I will also coordinate and supervise them to make sure the work is completed to your satisfaction. I operate on an hourly or day rate basis, and will quote you my fees upfront as I believe that in order to budget well, you need to know what your project is going to cost you.','The interior design services I offer','','Client reviews of my work','110-600','https://www.homify.co.uk/professionals/5749220/louise-misell-interiors','https://www.bark.com/en/company/louiselouisemisellinteriorscouk/aggmo/','{\"token\": \"EAAgDIOQeURcBAIh9kqZANN9ZBLrIOhZCZCDuL6YQZA52rxMTZAhPlqhWqfOgi8IfyuYzZBEW879UI3jCZCwWRZCReQ6h7fdkEGAQMZCv4TcfGTEh2yZB0nQEOOStFkn43CYdW0IRVmMOMbPbxCqZBw5yeKMd2iEk1Tan9l4ZD\"}','164508254214036','<p><span style=\"font-size:36px\">Clever use&nbsp;of colour, texture and pattern mixing used to create spaces with personality and warmth</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:48px\"><em>all designed around you</em></span></p>','<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">When I was little I spent most of my weekends rearranging my bedroom and dreaming up decorating ideas for it. As a teenager I even had a paint colour matched to a favourite purple earring! </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:36px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">I remember always being drawn to buildings, especially the sad looking, neglected ones, which I just wanted to save, and make beautiful again. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">I taught myself to sew and fell in love with fabrics, colours and textures. My theatre, film and television degree brought me to Wales and I would spend hours making curtains, cushions and anything I could to add personality to the rental properties I lived in.&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">I specialised in designing for the theatre and loved getting inside the minds of the characters I was designing for. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:36px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">I still use these skills today, with a lot of my clients commenting on my ability to understand them and draw out what they want, then translate these ideas into beautiful designs which reflect their personality.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">I was working in television when I decided to leave to raise my two boys. By then we had bought our first property and I had so much fun designing and renovating our homes that I knew it was time to rethink my career. </span></span><span style=\"font-size:36px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">I retrained as an interior designer, and looking back it&#39;s what I was born to do, </span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">but&nbsp;I&#39;m so glad that I spent time in the world of theatre and television learning how to apply my creative ideas in a practical way.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">Becoming a Home Design Stylist for John Lewis gave me a fantastic opportunity to work with hundreds of clients and help them bring their ideas to life. I loved the challenge of producing schemes to suit all tastes and budgets, but learned to share my creative vision for each space.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:36px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">It&#39;s so much fun combining each client&#39;s ideas with mine to create gorgeous interiors.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">I loved working with my John Lewis clients but really wanted to be able to help them turn our ideas into reality. Lots of clients get stuck when it comes to the practicalities of making changes to their homes and need someone to guide them through the process. By taking the next step and setting up my interior design business, I could help my clients through the stresses of planning and organising a project, and oversee all of the details from build to styling.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">I still love the thrill of starting a new project, and seeing the vast improvements that a well-designed space can make to a client&#39;s life. </span></span><span style=\"font-size:36px\"><span style=\"color:#335470\">There&#39;s nothing that makes me happier than when a client tells me that what we&#39;ve created feels like it&#39;s completely theirs.</span></span></p>','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Baskerville\"><span style=\"font-size:36px\">If it&#39;s time for you to inject some colour and personality into your space, and to have the home you really deserve,</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Baskerville\"><span style=\"font-size:48px\"><em>I&#39;d love to hear from you.</em></span></span></p>','','I offer a full range of interior design services and can help with anything from choosing paint colours to a complete redesign of your home or commercial space. I specialise in space planning to make your interiors work practically for you, and will work with you to help you define your interiors style. I travel to you and work across South Wales including Cardiff, Swansea, Newport, Penarth, Cowbridge, The Vale of Glamorgan and surrounding areas. Online interior design is also available.','{\"token\": \"5342fc8de14b60fad63c7610ff4cfe13\"}','50ae175bea','IMG_1116_full_size_wJLYU1W.jpg','IMG_1702_bigger.jpg','IMG_2160_cropped_tdOVbXd.jpg','IMG_2260_straightened_cropped3_lighter_CYb3qi1.jpg','IMG_2012cropped3.jpg','IMG_0937_adjusted_crop_smaller_x64wDg1.jpg','IMG_2220_adjusted_raJJbM1.jpg','<p><span style=\"color:#335470\"><span style=\"font-size:36px\">Firstly, I listen.</span><span style=\"font-size:24px\"> Designing someone&#39;s home is a very personal thing to do, so I spend time getting to know you, and how you and your family like to live. I gather as much information as I can, so that I can help you make the right choices for you.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#335470\"><span style=\"font-size:36px\">I will stop you from making expensive mistakes,</span><span style=\"font-size:24px\"> such as buying items which somehow just don&#39;t look quite as you imagined they would, or painting those walls for the <em>fifth</em> time.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#335470\"><span style=\"font-size:36px\">I am organised and plan everything carefully so that you don&#39;t have to.</span><span style=\"font-size:24px\"> My attention to detail and my experience of renovation mean that I can think on my feet, and solve those unforeseen issues which always come up.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#335470\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\">If you involve me at the beginning of your project, I can help with everything from planning where your plug sockets will go, to creating the right lighting scheme, to making sure your new sofa will fit through the door.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#335470\"><span style=\"font-size:36px\">I can guide you through the stress of a renovation.</span><span style=\"font-size:24px\"> I&#39;ll tell you the order in which things need to be done, and will help you plan so that you have all the answers when the builders need all your decisions right <em>now</em>.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#335470\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\">I am friendly and approachable, as </span><span style=\"font-size:36px\">I believe that everyone deserves access to good design.</span><span style=\"font-size:24px\"> I provide a truly personal service, producing designs which are as unique as my clients. I will give you honest, impartial advice. I&#39;m not selling anything apart from my ideas, so you won&#39;t be pushed into making any decision you&#39;re not comfortable with. All I offer is great design.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#335470\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\">There are so many choices out there, and sites like Pinterest and Instagram can be overwhelming without someone to help you navigate them. I work best when collaborating with my clients, so if you like my design style and think we will work well together, you&#39;ll get the best results from me.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:36px\">I&#39;ll help you turn bland and boring into somewhere which feels welcoming, interesting and inspiring - a real home.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#335470\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\">I have Public Liability insurance up to the value of &pound;1,000,000 and Professional Indemnity insurance up to the value of &pound;100,000.</span></span></p>');
